  "body": "## Description\r\n\r\nThe `--beacon-node` flag should be deprecated in v1.0.5, but seems completely broken. I'm running with `lighthouse-docker` and keep getting the following logs on startup\r\n```\r\nWARN Offline beacon node\r\nWARN Unable to connect to a beacon node\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Version\r\n\r\nDocker tag `v1.0.5`\r\n\r\n## Present Behaviour\r\n\r\nValidator not connecting to beacon node with `--beacon-node`\r\n\r\n## Expected Behaviour\r\n\r\nValidator connects to beacon node with `--beacon-node`\r\n\r\n## Steps to resolve\r\n\r\nRun `lighthouse-docker`\r\n",
